<br>
&quot;From the bottom of my heart Poseidon I wish to say thank you for the words that you have just uttered and graced my ears with. I have never before been so complimented by you! It honors me to hear that you perhaps think of me as powerful as you. Maybe perhaps I was wrong too, in saying that you were closed minded and a horrible person. You have kept the seas calm and a serene place for my dolphines to reside.&quot;<br>
<br>
He gets up from his seat and hugs Poseidon.<br>
<br>
&quot;Thank you Uncle...and you Hades.&quot;<br>
<br>
He smiles brightly.<br>
